cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.CV 

This paper deals with natural language processing and human-computer interaction, which are the main topics of the sub-categories cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which are relevant to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses eye gaze data, which could potentially involve computer vision techniques, making cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) another likely sub-category.
